I was trying to draw a triangle with this:

extends Node2D

func _draw():

```
draw_primitive(Vector2Array([Vector2(0,100),Vector2(100,300),Vector2(90,0)]),ColorArray([Color(1,0,0),Color(1,0,0),Color(1,0,0)])) 
pass
```

func _process(delta):
    update()
func _ready():
    set_process(true)

which doesnt  draw anything and romullox_x kindly provided workaround:

extends Node2D
var myColorArray = ColorArray()

func _draw():
    for color in [Color(1,0,0),Color(1,0,0),Color(1,0,0)]:
        myColorArray.push_back(color)
    draw_primitive([Vector2(0,100),Vector2(100,300),Vector2(90,0)], myColorArray)
pass

func _process(delta):
    update()
func _ready():
    set_process(true)
